Pivotal provides step-by-step upgrade guides for moving to supported versions of
Concourse for PCF.

<p class="note warning"><strong>Warning: </strong>
The BOSH deployment for Concourse for PCF v5.2.0 requires manifest changes.
These changes need to be applied regardless of whether you use the example from
<a href="https://github.com/concourse/concourse-bosh-deployment/tree/release/5.1.x/cluster/operations">concourse-bosh-deployment</a>
or your own manifest.
For more information on these manifest changes, see
<a href="./rn.html#breaking-manifest-520">Manifest</a> in the release notes.
</p>

